\c 10
\s Ubukhulu bukaModekhayi
\p
\v 1 Inkosi uAhasuwerusi yasibeka umthelo elizweni lezihlenge\add ni\add* zolwandle\x + Isa. 11.11. 24.15.\x*.
\v 2 Zonke-ke izenzo zamandla ayo lawengalo zayo\x + 9.29.\x*, lomlando wobukhulu bukaModekhayi\x + 4.7.\x*, inkosi eyamkhulisayo\x + 8.15. 9.4.\x*, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi eMede lePerisiya\x + 2.23. 6.1.\x*?
\v 3 Ngoba uModekhayi umJuda wayengowesibili enkosini uAhasuwerusi\x + 2 Lan. 28.7. Gen. 41.40.\x*, emkhulu phakathi kwamaJuda, ethandeka kulo inengi labafowabo\x + Dute. 33.24.\x*, edingela isizwe sakibo okuhle, ekhuluma ukuthula kuyo yonke inzalo yakhe\x + Neh. 2.10. Hlab. 122.8,9.\x*.
